{"tid":2339562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"施永青 聖誕快樂！！！","createTime":"2020-12-24T17:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T18:35:58.000Z","uid":7971,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"260209b27fad0e653ca534c4d08bd23400384666","tid":2339562,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，<strong><span class=\"red\">施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」</span></strong>，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"0bcd2d873a691ac9cb0d11ea26706825dd2dd7dc","tid":2339562,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08819619d02f714381985645db9d2a2873439330","tid":2339562,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330740faff5e6e0909beb4a7755fd4f53b1dc551","tid":2339562,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09994bb1fa65d60339559828b0ae2f35228e2417","tid":2339562,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src